Because with you, we make a difference!
Connect with other parents

Volunteer your time, at the school or at home, to make a difference in our school community

post_text:
Are you looking for an easy way to give back to JHES? Check this opportunity out at our local Country Mart grocery store in Holton! Thank you Julie Kirk for posting this on the JHCobras.net website!

Give Back to JHES

Jackson Heights Elementary School now has an account number at Holton Country Mart. If patrons choose to donate their shopping points to the school, money comes back to us. When you are checking out, all you have to do is let the cashier know that you would like to donate some points to JHES. Donations have to be done in 500 point increments.
